  <custodhist id="aspace_5cdaaa5c038443a0c7e77cb379ad119d">
    <head>Custodial History</head>
<p>The materials in the collection were originally owned by the Sutherland family and were later given to the daughter of Eddie Schultz, a former player and assistant coach for Sutherland and a family friend. The collection was later acquired by Dan Means and then by the University of Pittsburgh's Archives &amp; Special Collections.</p>  </custodhist>
