certificates, a proclamation for the Brooklyn Dodgers, a draft of Sutherland's statement on political ambitions, and a copy of a check for Sutherland and the City of Pittsburgh, all of which comes from the same scrapbook as the correspondence in the series.</p></scopecontent><c03 id="aspace_ref46_kzr" level="file"><did><unittitle>Certificates, programs, and other memorabilia</unittitle><unitid type="aspace_uri">/repositories/10/archival_objects/463935</unitid><container id="aspace_d771c135978d71efd11aead7b83f3ee2" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_0e06c95218fcb5a2dfac99172d2d50b5" parent="aspace_d771c135978d71efd11aead7b83f3ee2" type="folder">24</container></did></c03></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_ref2_pw8" level="series"><did><unittitle>Football</unittitle><unitid>II.</unitid><unitid type="aspace_uri">/repositories/10/archival_objects/463936</unitid><unitdate datechar="creation" normal="1930/1946" type="inclusive">1930-1946</unitdate></did><scopecontent id="aspace_c287088ab7f055ff73f4048125c85531"><head>Scope and Content Notes</head><p>This series contains material related to football teams coached by Jock Sutherland. It includes preparatory materials, such as a playbook from one of his former players, as well as partial game programs. The Mississippi State contract in this series comes from the same disbound scrapbook as the material in Series I., where there is also a copy of the contract.</p></scopecontent><c02 id="aspace_ref48_wpa" level="file"><did><unittitle>Pitt vs. Notre Dame football game program</unittitle><unitid type="aspace_uri">/repositories/10/archival_objects/463937</unitid><unitdate datechar="creation">October 25, 1930</unitdate><container id="aspace_510efc4a72e4ac80fdddab2ac0ae1914" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_6109fce3bd699b4ca97425b492f5da5f" parent="aspace_510efc4a72e4ac80fdddab2ac0ae1914" type="folder">25</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_ref49_gvv" level="file"><d